content.text: Ray is the Founder and CEO of Sthetic AI. He brings extensive experience in aesthetic clinic operations and industry management, with firsthand insight into patient decision-making workflows and clinic-side challenges.At Sthetic AI, Ray leads overall strategy, product direction, and go-to-market execution, bridging real-world clinical needs with the company’s AI and engineering capabilities.

Daniel is a Co-Founder of Sthetic AI, leading the research and development of core technologies including 3D/4D facial reconstruction, editing, and AI-driven aesthetic optimization.He graduated from the University of Waterloo, where he served as a research assistant with the Vision and Image Processing Research Group (VIP) and as a Research Council Officer at the  National Research Council of Canada (NRC), leading research in Computer Vision (CV) and Computer Graphics (CG).At Sthetic AI, Daniel is responsible for building the technical foundation of the platform, translating cutting-edge research into production-ready AI systems.

Evan is responsible for iOS application development and mobile system architecture at Sthetic AI, leading the implementation of the company’s mobile scanning and user-facing platform.He previously refactor the Avenza Maps, where he redesign the map engine with OpenGL and oversaw the development of large-scale, performance-critical mobile  applications.Prior to that, Evan was a Team Leader and Senior Mobile Developer at Alibaba Group,with experience spanning mobile applications, search-related systems, and high-traffic consumer platforms.At Sthetic AI, Evan focuses on building a robust iOS foundation integrating TrueDepth scanning, real-time processing, and production-grade mobile architecture.

children.html: Ray

children.name: Title
children.html: Founder

children.name: Description
children.html:
Ray is the Founder and CEO of Sthetic AI. He brings extensive experience in aesthetic clinic operations and industry management, with firsthand insight into patient decision-making workflows and clinic-side challenges.

At Sthetic AI, Ray leads overall strategy, product direction, and go-to-market execution, bridging real-world clinical needs with the company’s AI and engineering capabilities.

children.name: Name
children.html: Daniel

children.name: Title
children.html: Co-Founder | Head of AI

children.name: Description
children.html:
Daniel is a Co-Founder of Sthetic AI, leading the research and development of core technologies including 3D/4D facial reconstruction, editing, and AI-driven aesthetic optimization.

He graduated from the University of Waterloo, where he served as a research assistant with the Vision and Image Processing Research Group (VIP) and as a Research Council Officer at the National Research Council of Canada (NRC), leading research in Computer Vision (CV) and Computer Graphics (CG).

At Sthetic AI, Daniel is responsible for building the technical foundation of the platform, translating cutting-edge research into production-ready AI systems.

children.name: Name
children.html: Evan

children.name: Title
children.html: Lead iOS Engineer

children.name: Description
children.html:
Evan is responsible for iOS application development and mobile system architecture at Sthetic AI, leading the implementation of the company’s mobile scanning and user-facing platform.

He previously refactor the Avenza Maps, where he redesign the map engine with OpenGL and oversaw the development of large-scale, performance-critical mobile applications.


Prior to that, Evan was a Team Leader and Senior Mobile Developer at Alibaba Group,

with experience spanning mobile applications, search-related systems, and high-traffic consumer platforms.


At Sthetic AI, Evan focuses on building a robust iOS foundation integrating TrueDepth scanning, real-time processing, and production-grade mobile architecture.
